{'id': '934087104', 'text': "I apologize sincerely for the inconvenience you faced while attempting to book with us for New Year's night. Unfortunately, a system failure led to your details not being accurately reflected, and I regret any frustration this may have caused.

While we offered alternative venues due to our full capacity, I understand they did not meet your preferences. This situation is not reflective of our usual standards, and we are committed to preventing such issues in the future.

Your patience and understanding are greatly appreciated. If there's anything specific you'd like to discuss or if we can make amends, please reach out. We hope to regain your trust for a better experience in the future.", 'lang': 'en', 'publishedDate': '2024-01-15', 'responder': None, 'connectionToSubject': None}

{'id': '933893232', 'text': "Thank you for taking the time to share your feedback with us. We appreciate your kind words regarding the spacious rooms, balconies, and stunning sea views – we're pleased that you found our location and views deserving of a 5-star rating.

The hotel is gradually becoming operational after 3-4 years of uncertainty and economic challenges. We are working diligently to address the issues of painting, and it's worth noting that the peeling paint was a result of recent heavy rain and weather changes. The elevator has been awaiting parts for some time, but we anticipate its prompt resolution very soon. Please rest assured that we are actively addressing these maintenance issues to ensure a more pleasant stay for our guests. Your observations are invaluable, and we are committed to enhancing the overall condition of our facilities.

Regarding the disturbance caused by the all-night beach party, it is important to note that it was over 3 km away, and unfortunately, we had no control over this situation. However, we can assure you that such events are not a regular occurrence, and we sincerely apologize for any impact on your peaceful stay.", 'lang': 'en', 'publishedDate': '2024-01-13', 'responder': None, 'connectionToSubject': None}
